

=Description=

"The Farmer Landowner Match Program connects landowners seeking to have their land farmed with farmers seeking land. The farm operations involved with these matches include meat, vegetables, and crops. As of June 2012, CLC has had 25 successful matches, farming on over 1,000 acres of land, including Great Song Farm and Sparrowbush Farm."


